channel.title: Error
channel.description:
Hey guys, whenever my auto cache finished downloading I got this error in my cmd
java.io.FileNotFoundException: C:\.haizscape_file_store_32\Files\interface\36 0 0.png (The system cannot find the path specified) at java.io.FileOutputStream.open(Native Method) at java.io.FileOutputStream.(Unknown Source) at java.io.FileOutputStream.(Unknown Source) at client.unZipFile(client.java:3462) at client.downloadcache(client.java:3426) at client.method67(client.java:3498) at client.method6(client.java:6974) at Applet_Sub1.run(Applet_Sub1.java:47) at client.run(client.java:4583) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source)
and my cache also created another folder and placed all my files in there so idk why it did that, any help?
